episodes.title: Trying to recover from PTSD as a JW.
episodes.description:
This video explores the PTSD I mentioned having as one of Jehovah's Witnesses. It covers if that PTSD came from the religion/cult, and why it was more difficult to recover as part of it.

Thank you for stopping by.

#exjw #ptsdrecovery #jehovahswitnesses #traumarecovery

episodes.title: How I Woke Up: Another ExJW Story
episodes.description:
This is the story of how I began to realize I was in a cult and how I deconstructed my beliefs. All the pieces of my puzzle, though they may not make sense to all, are still the pieces of my puzzle. I hope this video speaks to some.

#exjw #jehovahswitnesses #lawofone #ramaterial #consciousness #spiritualawakening

episodes.title: Being Removed as One of Jehovah's Witnesses (with one week to appeal)
episodes.description:
In this video, I read a letter I had intended to send to the congregation which I was a part of. Before I could send this letter, an elder drove two hours to my husband's workplace to inform him of the decision of removal, without stating a cause. As far as I know they do not know of the videos I have created.

#exjw #jehovahswitnesses #cults #exmormon
